title: VA_-_First Impression
description:
First Impression is a masterpiece which will hit your head, soul and legs - hard!

As the name implies, this compilation is Fresh - A Contemporary Progressive-Psy-Tech-Trance Exploration.

Most artists on this compilation are new-comers - representing the new generation of Global Goa / Psy Trance. Continuing the way of AP Records in revealing the different aspects of Progressive-Psy-Trance through blending-groove mutations with Techno, House and Ambient - shaping up the most updated contemporary Trance and Electronic music.

As they say - we are the future. We designed this compilation to be a hard-kicking head-floor-pumper all the way through from start to end.

Style: Progress Trance

Released: July 2002/27

1. Trees   AUDIOMATIC
2. Raum und Zeit   MA-G-MA
3. Dark simple sigh   PTK
4. Complex stability   NUCLEAR RAMJET
5. Awakening   MA-G-MA
6. Intellectual property   ISMS
7. Trouble   CICERO
8. Spooky loops   ANALOG PUSSY
9. Third time (t-version)   SOLAR FIELDS
